metadata.name: Never give up / Marlon
metadata.description:
Welcome to my world, where people smile and turn away thinking I can't make it, they don't think I'm good enough, they think I'm wasting my time. But I know giving up isn't an option!

One day they'll see how wrong they were... when I make it, they'll hear me play and be inspired by me. 

Digitally created. Hires image size: 4000x4000px
